# Cursor Rules for ESLint Auto-fix on Save

# Enable ESLint auto-fix when saving files
- When saving TypeScript files, automatically run ESLint with --fix flag
- Apply ESLint rules: single quotes, no semicolons, 2-space indentation
- Format code according to the eslint.config.js configuration

# File patterns to apply ESLint to
- Apply to all .ts files in src/ directory
- Apply to all .js files in the project
- Exclude node_modules and build directories 